Package: blotbench
Title: Easy, reproducible Westen blot editing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Kai", "Aragaki", , "adamaragaki@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9458-0426"))
Description:
    blotbench includes a rudimentary visual image editor that helps you write
    reproducible, declarative, auditable code for editing western blots.
    Additionally, it provides tools for easily producing annotated,
    publication-ready images quickly.
